*.env
*.env.local
*.env.production
*.env.development
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.cer
*.crt
secrets/
credentials/
**/appsettings.Production.json
**/appsettings.Staging.json
**/*secrets*.json
**/*credentials*.json

# API Keys & Tokens (double-check!)
**/google-services.json
**/GoogleService-Info.plist
firebase-*.json

